{"tid":2117421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑狗係咪驚西瓜大王篤灰？","createTime":"2020-07-21T00:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T00:27:19.000Z","uid":9906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69d9bbb9760e5a4540dc07cea3fd1ca922132c40","tid":2117421,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"如果黑狗混入白衫人係真，<br />\n咁在場嘅人無可能唔知，<br />\n何況全部都係自己人，<br />\n邊個生面口一眼就認人得出啦。<br />\n仲未計大大隻狗證掛係心口。<br />\n至於之前拉咗果啲白衫人，<br />\n係雙方傾掂數嘅結果，<br />\n而且拉嘅只係爛頭卒。<br />\n雖然各個鏡頭都影晒西瓜大王有係現場，<br />\n但鄉黑根本有晒黑狗痛腳，<br />\n你想拉多啲人咩？<br />\n得，攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73067aa57701a5f9bc80162f623b53a37275b93","tid":2117421,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}